Name: Pulling No Punches
About the game: Pulling No Punches is a satirical game in the 2D beat'em up style with classic arcade influences and modern visuals. The game follows the fictional story of a global pandemic that engulfed the world and is being ignored by fanatics who do not believe that the disease is real. It is up to the main characters, 4 common citizens adequately protected with gloves and masks, to deal with these fanatics and solve the situation with the force of their own fists. ● 4 Co-op Local Multiplayer! ● 4 Characters with unique Unlockables and Moves! ● Use everything at your disposal to destroy your enemies: a wide variety of punches, kicks, grabs and headbutts! ● Handmade art painfully animated frame by frame!
